      <title>T. Rowe Price 称日元兑美元面临下跌 10% 的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/t-rowe-price-says-yen-is-at-risk-of-falling-10-against-dollar</link>
